{"tid":977984,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唔計食物同娛樂， 有冇人覺得出街為咗買衫買鞋買褲行一日好無謂","createTime":"2019-01-11T14:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T15:05:42.000Z","uid":110375,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ccce14ced49a87fc366e318d35bc3fc31591df4e","tid":977984,"uid":110375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:48:35.000Z","msg":"正常人每日都要返工㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n然後當放假嘅時候， 仲要曬啲無謂時間 去做一啲看似好有意義但係其實冇意義嘅事<br />\n<br />\n倒不如去學一啲興趣 或者去實踐一啲事情<br />\n<br />\n因為我覺得咁樣好戇鳩， 好似成個人生就係每日返工放工 放假就係為咗 買一啲衫褲鞋襪 裝飾品， 淨係識畀啲商家洗曬囉乜撚嘢放假就係要去shopping， 到頭來根本自己乜嘢都冇做過淨係買完一堆垃圾"},{"pid":"7900ce5c7eae9f1f4fc971759eb5535c83181cbf","tid":977984,"uid":89956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"咁衫褲鞋襪幾時買?"},{"pid":"e555ec0fe07865daf45c8ce93536fad28ecd8cb0","tid":977984,"uid":110375,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"7900ce5c7eae9f1f4fc971759eb5535c83181cbf","tid":977984,"uid":89956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"咁衫褲鞋襪幾時買?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"網上購物一次過買曬<br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得唔需要花咁多無謂時間去做呢啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n當然 耐唔耐 一兩次 冇乜所謂"},{"pid":"a0da9efd9e8da7f108ee3674142827ad05ac8425","tid":977984,"uid":89394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"咁你咪唔好撚著衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b219c30b7010caac6c8ddb2c749d0c26c27e209d","tid":977984,"uid":78429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"而家放假行街買衫又關你事"},{"pid":"6460e491110eb3213b02e48882b86ef67af92c8e","tid":977984,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:57:16.000Z","msg":"等樓主未來做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb773bb88fa599933176846c540e5ea60dd14e6","tid":977984,"uid":9335